<section id="faq" class="faq section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details>
        <summary class="faq-item">
          <span>What is Runora?</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
          <div class="faq-content"><p>This is an open-source personal finance tracker designed to help you manage your finances effectively. It provides tools and insights to track your spending, budget, and financial goals.</p></div>
      </details>
        <details>
            <summary class="faq-item">
              <span>Is this tracker free to use?</span>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="faq-content"><p>Yes, this personal finance tracker is completely free and open-source. You can use it without any hidden fees or subscription requirements.</p></div>
        </details>
      <details>
        <summary class="faq-item">
          <span>Where can I find the source code?</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
          <div class="faq-content"><p>The source code is hosted on GitHub. You can view and contribute to it by visiting <a href="https://github.com/frostdev7506/runora">https://github.com/frostdev7506/runora</a>.</p></div>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary class="faq-item">
          <span>How can I contribute to the project?</span>
           <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
           <div class="faq-content"><p>You can contribute by submitting bug reports, feature requests, or contributing code directly through the GitHub repository at <a href="https://github.com/frostdev7506/runora">https://github.com/frostdev7506/runora</a>. Any contribution to the project is much appreciated!</p></div>
      </details>
        <details>
            <summary class="faq-item">
               <span>What features does it offer?</span>
                 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="faq-content"><p>This finance tracker includes features such as tracking expenses, creating budgets, setting financial goals, and visualizing your financial data. More features are being added regularly!</p></div>
        </details>
      <details>
        <summary class="faq-item">
          <span>Is my data secure?</span>
           <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </summary>
           <div class="faq-content"><p>Yes, the security of your data is our top priority. This application is open source, so you can verify all of its code. Also, this application uses local storage so your data will be only on your computer.</p></div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .faq h2 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: rgb(var(--color-text));
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .faq-list {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-list details {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--color-primary), 0.2);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(var(--color-primary), 0.05);
  }

  .faq-list details[open] {
    background: rgba(var(--color-primary), 0.1);
  }

   .faq-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      cursor: pointer;
      list-style: none;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
     padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
   }

  .faq-list summary {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
    .faq-list summary::-webkit-details-marker {
        display: none;
    }


 .faq-list details:not([open]) .faq-content {
      overflow: hidden;
      max-height: 0;
 }
    .faq-list .faq-content {
        transition: max-height 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }
  .faq-list p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgb(var(--color-text-light));
      padding-top: 0.5rem;
  }

    .faq-item svg {
       transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }
   .faq-list details[open] summary svg {
      transform: rotate(180deg);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .faq h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .faq-list summary {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    }
</style>